Transmutation
Level: Ranger 4
Components: V, M
Casting Time: 1 Round
Range: Touch
Target: 1 Arrow or Bolt
Duration: 1 round per level
Save: Fortitude vs Paralysis
Spell Resistance: Yes

This spell is cast upon a arrow or bolt, transforming its head into blue ice. In addition to taking normal damage from the missile, the target takes 2d6 cold damage as well and is paralyzed. A succesful fortitude save negates the paralysis and the target gets a new save vs it each round.

